sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>Service Account Token
    participant LMESDriver as LMES Driver<br/>Sidecar Container
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant InfSvc as InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS/gRPC mTLS
    participant Secret as Kubernetes Secret

    Note over User,Secret: Flow 3: LM Evaluation Job Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event
    Operator->>Operator: Reconcile LMEvalJob
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job<br/>Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Job Created

    Note over LMESDriver: Job Pod Starts

    LMESDriver->>ModelReg: Download Model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Token/Credentials
    ModelReg-->>LMESDriver: Model Artifacts
    LMESDriver->>InfSvc: Run Evaluation Tasks<br/>mTLS Service Identity
    InfSvc-->>LMESDriver: Evaluation Results
    LMESDriver->>K8sAPI: Create Output Secret<br/>Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>LMESDriver: Secret Created

    Note over LMESDriver: Job Completes
